Shotgun Stories;;80;;90;;PG-13;;Backed by siblings Kid (Barlow Jacobs) and Boy (Douglas Ligon), Son Hayes (Michael Shannon) tells the attendees at his father's funeral that he and his brothers hated the dead man, then spits on his grave. This triggers a battle with the siblings' half brothers, which soon leaves Kid dead and Son seriously hurt. As the half brothers stockpile weapons for what they assume will be a deadly encounter, Boy visits them and suggests an end to the fighting.;;Mystery & thriller,Drama;;Jeff Nichols;;2007;;Michael Shannon,Douglas Ligon,Barlow Jacobs,Natalie Canerday,Glenda Pannell;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shotgun_stories